2010-02-03  Jonathan Kamens  <jik@kamens.brookline.ma.us>

	* Release 10.00-beta-3.

	* Strip empty headers from messages before posting them, because
	some NNTP servers choke on empty headers.

2009-12-30  Jonathan Kamens  <jik@kamens.brookline.ma.us>

	* Release 10.00-beta-2.

	* Fixes to make XRN compile and run properly on 64-bit machines.

	* Server timeouts can cause NNTP error code 205 as well as 503.
	Therefore, accept 205 when attempting to detect and recover from
	timeouts.

